Class ImException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • info.guardianproject.otr.app.im.engine.ImException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ImException
extends java.lang.Exception
    A generic exception that is thrown by the IM engine. If it's caused by an error condition returned by the IM server, an IMError is associated with it.
    See Also:
